    {
      "id": "data_flow",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 490,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "IProgressionManager\n  ├─ .GetAllLevelRecords() → List<LevelRecord>\n  │    └─ LevelNumber, CityName, Mood, Stars\n  ├─ .CurrentLevel → int\n  └─ .IsLevelCompleted(n) → bool\n\n       ↓ builds\n\nRoadmapNodeData (NEW class)\n  ├─ LevelNumber, State, StarsEarned, IsBoss\n  ├─ IslandSprite  ← from RoadmapAssets SO\n  ├─ FlipX         ← ShouldFlip(levelNumber)\n  └─ WorldPosition ← GetNodePosition()\n\n       ↓ renders\n\nIsland GO + WorldSpace Canvas (badges, stars)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2026,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2026,
